                                                                        <p>6. From him, from Salma, who said, ‘I complained at Al-Medina with intense complaints (pains), so I went to Abu Al-Hassan (a.s.). So he (a.s.) said to me: ‘I (a.s.) see you as pale?’ I said, ‘Yes’. He (a.s.) said: ‘Eat the leek’. So I ate it, and was free from it’.</p>
