                                                                    <div class="form-group">
                                                                        <p>Hadith to report:</p>
                                                                        <p>16. From him, from Muhammad Bin Al Waleed, from yunus Bin Yaqoub who said, ‘I saw Abu Al-Hassan (a.s.) the First cutting the leek by its roots, so he (a.s.) washed it with the water and ate it’.</p>
